import React from 'react'
import {
    InfoContainer,
    InfoWrapper,
    InfoRow,
    Colum1,
    TextWrapper,
    TopLine,
    Heading,
    Subtitle,
    BtnWrap
} from './InfoSectionElements'
import {Button} from '../ButtonElement'

const InfoSection = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <InfoContainer >
                <InfoWrapper>
                    <InfoRow>
                        <Colum1>
                            <TextWrapper>
                                <TopLine>Top Line</TopLine>
                                <Heading>Heading</Heading>
                                <Subtitle>Subtitle</Subtitle>
                                <BtnWrap>
                                    <Button to='Home '>Button</Button>
                                </BtnWrap>
                            </TextWrapper>
                        </Colum1>
                    </InfoRow>
                </InfoWrapper>
            </InfoContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default InfoSection;
